  "remarks": "JSC Integral is a Belarusian state-owned manufacturer of semiconductors, integrated circuits and other high technology goods with particular importance for the Belarusian economy and the defence sector. JSC Integral is located in the Minsk Free Economic Zone, established by the Belarusian Government. Entities established in the Minsk Free Economic Zone profit from various financial advantages. Therefore, JSC Integral is benefitting from the Lukashenka regime.",
